## Keyboard shortcuts

- Ctrl+1 — Home  
- Ctrl+2 — Learn  
- Ctrl+3 — Track  
- Ctrl+4 — Insights  
- Ctrl+5 — Progress  
- Ctrl+6 — Tools  
- Ctrl+7 — Settings

---

## Tech stack

- Python 3.11+
- PyQt5
- SQLite + SQLAlchemy ORM
- python‑dotenv
- keyring
- pytest, mypy, ruff, black

---

## Setup

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -e .
```

Create a local `.env` from `.env.example`.

---

## Run

```bash
python -m anxiety_app.main
```

---

## Tests

```bash
pytest
```

---

## Notes

- AI insights/feedback are optional. If no API key is configured, the app returns stubbed insights.
- All data stays local unless you choose to generate AI insights or tool feedback.
